name: Josephine Creek (Upper)
description:
Introduction

Head water drainage of Josephine Creek. It looks to have potential from Angeles Forest Highway but disappointed we where

Approach

The trailhead is at Clear Creek Junction (Angeles Crest and Angeles Forest Highways). Park here and hike down Angeles forest highway a short distance to Josephine Peak Road. Through the gate and then the long slog up the road on the south facing side of Josephine peak 2.45 miles, 1352ft up the road it cuts through the ridge and continues on the north side 1.36 mi 642ft

Background
